snippet.title: Johnny Depp Takes Girlfriend Amber Heard on The Lone Ranger Press Tour | POPSUGAR News
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp had fun after the Moscow premiere of The Lone Ranger. Following a stint on the red carpet alongside costar Armie Hammer, Johnny hit the town with his girlfriend, Amber Heard! We're recapping Amber and Johnny's night out and finding out why he spoke with David Letterman this week about men being "simpletons."
